-- Disney's Pixar Pushes Boundaries of Animation (Audio)
-- B y
-- 2013-03-06T12:06:57Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-03-06/disney-s-pixar-pushes-boundaries-of-animation-audio-.html
Disney's Pixar won the 2013 Oscar 
for Best Animated film for Brave. The company, which created 
characters such as Buzz Lightyear, Lightning McQueen and Nemo 
adds another to the roster, Merida,
a teenage princess who causes chaos in her kingdom. Bloomberg's 
Carole Zimmer reports on the one of the world's most successful 
animation companies. (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 05:57
 